[Notice of Your Right to Opt-out of Sale/Sharing
You have the right to Opt-out of PACSUN sharing your information with Third Parties. PACSUN recognizes Opt-Out Preference Signals which is a configuration you can make in your browser that communicates with our website. Depending on your browser provider, you may be able to automatically Opt-out of processing your Personal Information within your browser's settings. If your browser does not allow for OOPS, the easiest way to Opt-out of our sharing your personal information with Third Parties is to use the "Do Not Sell/Share my Personal Information" signal linked here. If that is not convenient, you may also submit a request to opt-out by submitting a Personal Information Request. You may also call us at 1 (877) 372-2786.]